      "file_path": "packages/policy-api-docker/src/main/docker/Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 8,
      "message": "Hi Jorge,\nDo you mean we'd better to keep the POLICY_HOME as the parent image?\nIf so, I think the policy-api.sh should be updated, because it use the path /opt/app/policy/api as the location of base software now.",
